### Variables
@urlLocal = http://localhost:8080/api/v1/challenges
@contentType = application/json

### POST Challenge 1
POST {{urlLocal}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "challengeDate": "2024-09-20 16:00:00.000",
