### GET all
GET {{urlLocal}}


### GET all from a player
GET {{urlLocal}}?idPlayer=66f1dadecb49ee369f060fb1


### PUT
# @prompt challenge
PUT {{urlLocal}}/{{challenge}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "challengeDate": "2024-09-20 17:00:00.000",
    "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

### DELETE
# @prompt challenge
DELETE {{urlLocal}}/{{challenge}}


